title: JoomlaUX Constru - Construction Joomla Theme
description:
Constru is the modern Engineering and Construction Joomla Template. Built with Bootstrap 3, HTML5, K2 and available on Joomla 3.x, Constru is tailored to stand out from other construction templates around yet still function well for any construction, builder, engineering, contractor and other related business website.

The template is totally responsive and retina ready on every high-resolution device. Included 4 homepage variations, 4 preset styles and various shortcodes, Constru brings to your hand all features you need: Project listing and Project single, Service, Testimonial, Blog and Contact, Newsletter. It is empowered with useful extensions: Revolution Slider, JUX Portfolio, Acymailing and JUX Social Tab.
Let's see what is the best about this template
